HOW TO RUN
──────────
Just double-click any .html file to open it in your browser.
No server, no internet, no installation needed.
 
Or in VS Code:
  1. Install the "Live Server" extension (optional, but nicer)
  2. Right-click the .html file → "Open with Live Server"
  OR simply press Ctrl+Shift+P → "Open in Default Browser"

  ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TASK 2 — Task2_MusicGeneration.html
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Tool: AI Music Generation
Tech: Markov Chain sequence generation + Music Theory rules
      + Web Audio API for real playback + Piano Roll canvas
Genres: Classical, Jazz, Electronic, Blues, Ambient, Lo-fi
Moods: Melancholic, Uplifting, Mysterious, Energetic,
       Peaceful, Dramatic, Playful, Romantic
Features:
  • Markov Chain transition matrices per genre
  • Music theory scales (major, minor, dorian, blues, pentatonic)
  • Tempo, complexity, length, octave sliders
  • Animated piano roll visualizer
  • Real audio playback via Web Audio API (oscillators)
  • Live waveform visualizer
  • Export MIDI info as text file with Python snippet